HEADWORD: Pictorial
<hw>Pic*to"ri*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pictorius</ets>, fr. <ets>pictor</ets> a painter, fr.
<ets>pingere</ets> to paint. See <er>Paint</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or
